text: 選択したウマ娘のピース。育成ウマ娘の解放や才能開花などに使用できる。
"translate": A piece of the selected Uma Musu.\nCan be used to obtain or upgrade Uma Musu.

text: 育成ウマ娘の解放や才能開花などで使用。\n育成ウマ娘ごとの願いが結晶化された専用のピース。
"translate": Used to obtain Uma Musu and develop their talents.\nA special piece with the crystallized wishes of a horse girl.

text: 特上にんじんハンバーグ
182 & 170 - Mostly horse names (already translated by 6) with some NPCs, listed here
